      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Mantas ar Mello Wallo-\ndu kraht/ tas irr weena welta\nNeleetiba to/ kas to Nahwi\nmekle.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. To Besdeewigo Laupi-\nschana darra tohs bailsigs/ ta-\npehz ka tee aisleeđs darriht/ kas\nteefa irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Tas Wihrs kas pahrwehr-\ntitu Zeltu staiga/ tas irr fiveſch/\nbet kas ſchkihts irr/ ta patcha\nDarbs irr pareifs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Labbaft irr us Jumtu kab-\nda Raktā dshwoht/ ne ka pee\nweenas Rehjejas Seewas weenā\nNamina kohpa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Ta Besdeewiga Dweh-\nfete eekahro Launu/ winna Tu-\nwaks ne dabbu Schehlastibu\npreekſch winna Azzim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Kad tas Mehdtajs foḥ-\ndihts tohp/ tad tohp tas Neno-\njehga gudrs/ bet kad tas Gudrs\ntohp pamahzihts/ tad peenemi\nwinſch to Sinnaschanau.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tas Taifnajs turrahs\ngudri prett ta Besdeewiga Nam-\ntu/ (kad Deews) tohs Bes-\ndeewigus Nelaimibā gahſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Kas fawn Auiſi aisbahſch\npreekſch ta Nabbaga Kleegſcha-\nnas/ tas arridsan faufs/ un ne\ntaps paſtanſihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Steppena Dahwana kluf-\nfina to Bahrsibu/ un Dahwa-\nna Klehpi eedohta to bahrgu Ap-\nduſmotchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Taifnain Preeks irr dar-\nriht/ kas Teeta irr/ bet teem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Zilweks kas no ta Zel-\ntahs Gudribas blandahs/ ta-\njaſaleek ſtarр to Nomirruſch\nPulku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Kaß Kahribu mihte/ ta-\npaliks nabbags/ un kas Wih-\nun Etji mihte/ tas ne taps bag-\ngate.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Tas Besdeewigajs ir-\npar Isglabbfchann ta Taiſnu-\nnodohts/ un tas Wiltneeks pa-\nteim Rahineem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Labbaft irr tukſchā Sem-\nmē dshwoht/ neka pee Rehjeja-\nun duſmitgas Seewas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Ta Gudra Dshwohti tr-\nweena mihtiga Manta un Etje-\nbet weens gettigs Zilweks isteh-\nre to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Kaß pehz Tatsutbas un-\nLabbadarrischanas dsennahs/ at-\nraddihs to Dshwibu/ Taifnibu\nun Gehdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Weens Gudrs usſem to\nWarreno Pilstahtu/un apaahſch\nto Stiprumu / us ko wiſch\npatanjahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Kas fawn Mutti un fa-\nwu Mehli farga/ tas paſarga\nfawu Dwehfeli no Bailehu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Kas leppojahts un greſ-\nnojahts/ ta Wahrdā irr Mehdi-\ntajs/ jo tas zaar Duſmitbu fa-\nwu Lepnibu parahta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Ta Eekahroschana ta\nSlinka nokauj winnu/ jo win-\nna Rohkas leedsahs strahdabt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Zaar augotchu Deruu\nwiſch\n"
    }
  ],
